description: Sweet Ride Ice Cream is a vintage ice cream bike and mobile ice cream parlor serving locally produced super-premium ice cream, custom made ice cream cookie sandwiches, floats and classic ice cream novelties! Our goal is to deliver quality ice cream in style to you! Visit the Sweet Ride bike and mobile ice cream parlor about town to grab yourself a delicious ice cream treat, or have us add that special unique touch to your next party!
name: Sweet Ride Ice Cream, LLC
